标题：小船、大船（boat, ship）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אֳנִי</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’oni)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:26\">1KI 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:27\">1KI 9:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:11\">1KI 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:22\">1KI 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:22\">1KI 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:22\">1KI 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:21\">ISA 33:21</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אֳנִיָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’oniyah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:13\">GEN 49:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:68\">DEU 28:68</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:17\">JDG 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:27\">1KI 9:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:49\">1KI 22:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:49\">1KI 22:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:50\">1KI 22:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:18\">2CH 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:18\">2CH 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:21\">2CH 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:21\">2CH 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:36\">2CH 20:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:36\">2CH 20:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:37\">2CH 20:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:26\">JOB 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:8\">PSA 48:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:26\">PSA 104:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:23\">PSA 107:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:19\">PRO 30:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:14\">PRO 31:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:16\">ISA 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.